Package com.risk.phases

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Game
    Abstract Class for Game Phase
    GameExecuteOrder
    Game execute order executes the orders of each player in a round robin manner
    GameIssueOrder
    Game issue order allows players to issue their orders
    GameStartup
    Game startup allows map loading, assigning players and countries functionalities
    GameStartupTest
    The type Game startup test is to test that only valid commands in Game Startup phase are allowed.
    MapEdit
    Abstract class for Map Edit phase
    Phase
    Phase Class is the parent class for the State Pattern implementation
    PhasesTestSuite
    Test Suite for Phases tests
    PostMapLoad
    Post map load phase allows methods like showmap, validatemap, savemap and other editmap functionalities
    PreMapLoad
    Pre map load phase only allows editmap function to load the map
    PreMapLoadTest
    The Pre map load test is used to verify that only allowed commands in Pre Map Load phase are allowed while others are invalid
